casebody.head_matter:
Edward Faye PARKS, Petitioner,
v.
Bruno STOLC, Warden, et al.
No. 18-9528
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
